item.content:encoded:
House Clean Up 3D is a simulation cleaning game. It has 9 scenes for you to clean, which are a fence, sculpture, trampoline, pool, robot, fountain, ground, car, and dining table. You can experience all the housework in this game.
On PC and mobileClick to learn how to clean.
